	* Create a new intermediate node class (tree-node) for nodes
	having parent, child nodes and attribute nodes. Inherit sgml-node,
	ldap-node from this new class.

(node-set-parent-recursive! node)

Recursively set parent for all node children.

Use this machanism to create trees